        <h3>Titanic</h3>
        <p class="Genre">Romance/Drama/Tradegy/Action</p>
        <p>
          Titanic is a 1997 American epic romance and disaster film directed,
          written, produced, and co-edited by James Cameron. Incorporating both
          historical and fictionalized aspects, it is based on accounts of the
          sinking of the RMS Titanic, and stars Leonardo DiCaprio and Kate
          Winslet as members of different social classes who fall in love aboard
          the ship during its ill-fated maiden voyage. Also starring are Billy
          Zane, Kathy Bates, Frances Fisher, Gloria Stuart, Bernard Hill,
          Jonathan Hyde, Victor Garber, and Bill Paxton.
        </p>
